# Title: File Download And Execution Via IEExec.EXE
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-05-16
# Level: high
# Description: Detects execution of the IEExec utility to download and execute files
# MITRE Tactic: Command and Control
# Tags: attack.command-and-control, attack.t1105
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_ieexec_download.yml

CommandLine IN ("*http://*", "*https://*") Image="*\\IEExec.exe" OR OriginalFileName="IEExec.exe"